.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, dahlia
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, superhero
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, van
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Flower           | dahlia | daisy     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime          | superhero |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Transport     | van            | bus       |

 